    "body": "```powershell\n❯ starship timings\n\n Here are the timings of modules in your prompt (>=1ms or output):\n git_branch     -  2644ms  -   \"[ main]\"\n git_status     -   931ms  -   \"[+⇡]\"\n python         -   447ms  -   \"[🐍 v3.12.4]\"\n nodejs         -   355ms  -   \"[ v22.13.1]\"\n battery        -    10ms  -   \"\"\n pijul_channel  -     7ms  -   \"\"\n package        -     1ms  -   \"[📦 v0.1.0]\"\n username       -     1ms  -   \"\"\n directory      -    <1ms  -   \"WBH\\eve-multitools\\eve-multitools \"\n line_break     -    <1ms  -   \"\\n\"\n character      -    <1ms  -   \"❯ \"\n```\n🤔So it seems that the cause is my git repo? I'll try this on an empty repo later.\n\n> Are you using a build using the `release` profile for starship?\n\nYes.",
