    "updated_at": "2025-08-01T06:39:44Z",
    "body": "Problems solved :(.\nThis is caused by somewhat recent Windows update. MS PC Manager starts to monitor .git files, which lead to decreased Git performance. This is *not* a starship bug but a f*king Windows update.\n\nFor others experiencing this, check your anti-virus software :(.",
